{"tid":482398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有錢就任性】富豪後園建一級方程式跑道","createTime":"2017-11-28T06:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T10:42:14.000Z","uid":28366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"909f8f721b7344339eaee3a5cb32ece81981ea83","tid":482398,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/143046_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F143046_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e1448db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一般人會在自己住所後園興建泳池、菜園或燒烤場，但有錢便可以任性，美國紐約一名熱愛賽車的富豪，竟然花了300萬美元（2,340萬港元），在自己豪宅後園興建一個符合職業標準的跑道，讓他可以女友、朋友在家中風馳電掣。<br />\n<br />\n52歲的威齊（Alan Wilzig）於2004年以7.26億美元（56億港元）出售自己的信託公司，翌年花了335萬美元（2,613萬港元）買了中幢150年歷史的豪宅，他不諱言買這幢房子就是為了建跑道。他花費了300萬美元（2,340萬港元）建造這條賽車跑道，跑道長1.8公里、寬12米（40呎）、9個彎道、24米（80呎）高度變化、草地覆蓋邊界及圍欄。威齊形容這是全球唯一符合職業標準的純私人用一級方程式賽車跑道。<br />\n<br />\n興建跑道的消息甫傳出，鄰居都擔心噪音問題，法院於2007年一度頒禁令興建，但最終跑道在2010年5月竣工。其後他除了與好友一齊賽車外，便是與23歲女友萊費（Clemence Lapeyre）一起享受駕車樂趣，他盛讚女友與他一樣沉迷賽車，每天都會與女友到跑道互相追逐。<br />\n<br />\n他解釋自己想興建跑道，緣於一位朋友駕駛電單車，幾乎因交通意外死亡，令他決定不再在街上開快車。「當（我）駕著電單車跑了16萬公里平安無事，我意識到只是時間問題，隨時有人駕駛一輛漂亮的車撞向我。」<br />\n<br />\n威齊可謂名副其實的賽車發燒友，他更擁有一間3層高的「賽車博物館」，展示他500萬美元（3,900萬港元）的汽車及電單車收藏。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/143103_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F143103_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b189bc96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/143106_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F143106_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4f226231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/143108_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F143108_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7fb89738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171128/57511004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171128%2F57511004&d=Okuil18rNQnAbjPkGiDrmkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=2e872720\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171128%2F57511004&h=30e587c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171128/57511004</a>"},{"pid":"b6cd5dd3ff9585cc94cc02785f5840b9f789efa2","tid":482398,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a884c19aea2bc0ced72c151c7c0d7b19dcf51a2b","tid":482398,"uid":10692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"524b54787e519ac6ab8349fd1949af61814d9b5b","tid":482398,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">獅子山籠屋精神五十年不變</span></span> (2017年 香港人均居住面積為10平米，僅為亞洲城市1/3大)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港畜與豬</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/193658_d8e6e8bd47a483f66d373a59ca85ce86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F193658_d8e6e8bd47a483f66d3